3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of MLP neural networks for recognition can be considered as an application of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper deals with the classification of gradient change features, which can be considered as a form of feature extraction. Feature extraction is an important step in information retrieval.
